Labyrinth-Plugin-Album
======================

Labyrinth is a Website Management Framework. This distribution enables Labyrinth
to provide the features of a photo gallery.

This distributions contains all the photo album handling functionality used
to incorporate galleries into Labyrinth. This includes the templates, SQL,
parameter validation and dispatch tables.

INSTALLATION

See the INSTALL file for full instructions.

DEPENDENCIES

  File::Path
  Image::Size
  Labyrinth
  Labyrinth::Plugin::Hits

